text: Christophe Caresche (born September 2, 1960 in Arcachon) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the city of Paris, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:People from Arcachon Category:Politicians from Paris Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic
